        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streak turns your Gmail inbox into a fully functional CRM. No separate app. No new login. Just your email, upgraded with pipelines, mail merge, and automations that live where you already work.",
